%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
timeline
    title Image Segmentation Evolution (2012-2024)
    section CNN Era
        2012 : AlexNet - Deep CNN revolution
        2014 : FCN - First end-to-end pixel prediction
        2015 : U-Net - Skip connections for biomedical
             : DeepLab v1 - Atrous convolutions + CRF
        2016 : 3D U-Net - Volumetric segmentation
             : V-Net - Dice loss for medical
        2017 : PSPNet - Pyramid pooling
             : Mask R-CNN - Instance segmentation
        2018 : UNet++ - Nested dense skip connections
             : Attention U-Net - Attention gating
             : DeepLab v3+ - ASPP + encoder-decoder
    section Transformer Era
        2020 : ViT - Vision Transformer
        2021 : TransUNet - CNN-Transformer hybrid
             : Swin Transformer - Shifted windows
             : Swin-Unet - Pure transformer encoder-decoder
             : SegFormer - Efficient transformer
             : nnU-Net - Self-configuring (Nature Methods)
    section Universal & Foundation
        2022 : Mask2Former - Universal masked attention
             : UNETR - ViT encoder for 3D
        2023 : OneFormer - One model all tasks
             : SAM - Segment Anything Model
        2024 : SAM 2 - Images and videos
             : MedSAM2 - 3D medical volumes as video
